<h2>💬 Sentences</h2>

<table>

<tr>
<th>English</th>
<th>Konkani (RSB) - Kannada</th>
<th>Konkani (RSB) - Devanagari</th>
</tr>

<tr>
<td>What is your name?</td>
<td>ತುಜೆ ನಾಂವ್ ಕಾಯಿ?</td>
<td>तुझे नांव काय?</td>
</tr>

<tr>
<td>How are you?</td>
<td>ತು ಕಸೊ ಆಸಾ?</td>
<td>तु कसो आसा?</td>
</tr>

<tr>
<td>I am fine.</td>
<td>ಹಾಂವ್ ಬರೊ ಆಸಾಂ.</td>
<td>हांव बरो आसां.</td>
</tr>

</table>

