<section id="history">

<h2>📜 History</h2>

<p>
Rajapur Saraswat Brahmins (RSB) are a Konkani-speaking community found mainly in Karnataka, Goa and Maharashtra. Their language is a form of Konkani written in Kannada and Devanagari scripts.
</p>

